# Project Overview

This project is a professional website for an exterior construction company.

The goal is to create a modern website that helps the company:
- attract direct customers
- showcase completed projects
- maintain contractor partnerships


# Business Context

The company specializes in:

- siding installation
- aluminum exterior wrapping
- window capping
- gutters
- exterior finishing
- shutters


# Technology

Use:

- React
- Vite
- JavaScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion


# Design Goals

The website should feel:

- professional
- trustworthy
- modern
- high quality

Avoid:
- excessive animations
- flashy startup designs


# Coding Style

Prefer:

- reusable components
- clean folder structure
- mobile-first responsive design
- semantic HTML